  "texts": [
    "This could be of interest to researchers and practitioners across disciplines ranging from political psychology to organizational behavior.",
    "Second, the research expands our understanding of word embeddings, which bear some similarity to human semantic memory 31.",
    "They are known to encode words' meanings 42, including information about group stereotypes [43] [44] [45].",
    "Our results show that they also capture individual differences, like individuals' perceived personality traits.",
    "Our studies add to the growing body of social science research utilizing LLMs."
